Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,In a world where
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,AI is transforming how
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.06,0:00:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,we interact with technology,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.64,0:00:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,understanding chatchipity apps is
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.28,0:00:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,essential,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.04,0:00:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,with Alpic developing over
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.48,0:00:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,two dozen chatchipity apps
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.01,0:00:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,in just three months,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.33,0:00:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,this space is rapidly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.46,0:00:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,evolving.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.33,0:00:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's dive into some
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.24,0:00:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,crucial lessons that every
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.66,0:00:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,developer should know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.83,0:00:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Building chatchipity apps isn't
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.71,0:00:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,like traditional web development
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.23,0:00:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.85,0:00:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The introduction of an
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.76,0:00:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,AI model creates a
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.94,0:00:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,complex triadic relationship between
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.94,0:00:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,the user,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.69,0:00:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,the UI, and the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.55,0:00:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,model itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.28,0:00:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,This means developers need
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.87,0:00:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,to rethink their approach
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.28,0:00:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,to managing information flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.92,0:00:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Alpic's journey provides us
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.20,0:00:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,with 15 essential lessons
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.71,0:00:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,distilled from real world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.93,0:00:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,app development.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.06,0:00:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,For instance, patterns that
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.11,0:00:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,work well in traditional
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.25,0:00:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,apps,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.85,0:00:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,like just in time
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.78,0:00:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,data fetching can actually
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.15,0:00:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,hinder user experience in
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.57,0:00:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,chatchipity apps.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.74,0:00:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This is vital for
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.57,0:00:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,developers to understand as
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.97,0:00:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,they design their applications.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.67,0:00:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,To tackle these unique
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.52,0:00:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,challenges,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.39,0:00:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Alpic introduced the Skybridge
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.64,0:00:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Framework,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.47,0:00:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,an open source tool
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.39,0:00:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,designed to assist developers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.96,0:00:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This framework allows for
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.32,0:00:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,better management of the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.39,0:00:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,user interactions
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.15,0:00:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and UI updates, leading
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.85,0:00:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,to a more fluid
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.67,0:01:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.53,0:01:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,With the right tools,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.56,0:01:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,developers can create engaging
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.06,0:01:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and effective applications more
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.50,0:01:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.04,0:01:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The lessons learned from
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.87,0:01:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Alpic's development process are
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.37,0:01:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,crucial
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.78,0:01:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,as we move into
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.65,0:01:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the future of app
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.59,0:01:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,development.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.45,0:01:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,As AI continues to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.59,0:01:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,evolve, so will the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.40,0:01:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,methodologies we use to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.81,0:01:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,create applications.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.20,0:01:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember, embracing these lessons
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.84,0:01:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and utilizing frameworks like
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.42,0:01:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Skybridge
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.92,0:01:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,will set you apart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.95,0:01:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,in this exciting journey.
